        },
        {
            "id": "s_l5_4",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Two Steps ✌️",
            "content": "Note that we `await` effectively **twice**:\n\n1. Wait for connection (`fetch`).\n2. Wait for downloading the body (`response.json()`)."
        },
